title: Grateful Dead Live at Oakland Auditorium Arena on 1980-12-26
description:
Set 1

Alabama Getaway-> Promised Land, They Love Each Other, CC Rider, Althea, Cassidy, Peggy-O, Lost Sailor-> Saint Of Circumstance-> Deal

Set 2

Scarlet Begonias-> Fire On The Mountain, Samson & Delilah, Ship of Fools, Playin' In The Band-> Drums-> Not Fade Away-> Black Peter-> Around & Around-> Good Lovin', E: U.S. Blues

SEVA Benefit

reviews.review_text: Good show Good show.  Miss the boys a lot. Never saw the dead til 85 and I love listening to shows like this one.

Good show I particularly like Scarlet>Fire, Samson and yes Jerry is crispy on Ship of Fools.
SEVA=Service!
